data.name: AAK Personal Care
data.description: AAK Personal Care is dedicated to providing innovative, value-adding solutions to our customers, enabling them to achieve sustainable business results. We collaborate with customers to apply our in-depth knowledge and expertise in oils and fats within food applications to develop value-adding vegetable oil solutions. We offer a wide range of raw materials and broad process capabilities across many industries, including chocolate and confectionery, bakery, dairy, special nutrition, food service, personal care and more.

data.name: Akofine R
data.description: Akofine R™ is composed of fully saturated, deodorized high erucic Rapeseed oil (Brassica napus). This is a high melting all vegetable fat offered in powdered form for convenient use.

data.name: Akoline MCM
data.description: Akoline MCM™ is a mono / diglyceride of medium chain fatty acids (primarily caprylic and capric acids). Akoline MCM™ conforms to USP-NF, and has GRAS status according to FDA 21 CFR § 184.1505. Akoline MCM™ is liquid to semi-solid at room temperature.

data.name: Akofine P
data.description: Akofine P™ is composed of fully saturated, deodorized vegetable oil. This is a high melting all vegetable fat offered in powdered form for convenient use.

data.name: Akosoft 36
data.description: Akosoft 36™ is obtained by transesterification and deodorisation of vegetable oils. Akosoft 36™ conforms to EP (Hard Fat). Akosoft 36™ is a Eco-friendly, moisturizing oleogel for skin and hair care, including fragrance-free formulations. Suitable as an alternative to light petrolatum gels.

data.name: Akogel
data.description: Akogel™ is a blend of refined, hydrogenated and deodorized food grade vegetable oils and fats, carefully selected to obtain an oxidation stable product with a semi-solid consistency. This vegetable gel is developed to be an alternative to petroleum jellies. Akogel™ has a neutral odor.

data.name: High Oleic Brassica Oil
data.description: High Oleic Brassica Oil is a refined rapeseed oil with low linolenic and high oleic acid content. High Oleic Brassica Oil has high oxidative stability and is clear at room temperature.

data.name: Akocare
data.description: Akocare™ Coconut Oil comes from a traceable supply chain where AAK is working on improving the trading and production conditions at origin. For example, it has been confirmed that primates are not involved in the harvesting of the coconuts, which makes the coconut oil suitable for vegans.

data.name: LIPEX® 205™

summary.name: Synonyms
items: Butyrospermum parkii butter, Cropure Liquid Vegela, Shea butter, Shea fats, Shea oil, Shea olein

data.description: Lipex 205™ is a liquid cosmetic ingredient composed of refined, fractionated and deodorized vegetable oil taken from the fruit of the Shea tree (Butyrospermum parkii). Lipex 205™ contains a relatively high level of unsaponifiables.

data.name: Akocare™ Coconut RA SG
data.description: Akocare™ Coconut RA SG is traceable to farmer level in Indonesia and it is refined from crude, using a natural, chemical- free process.  To obtain coconut oil (Cocos nucifera) the white flesh of coconuts is first pressed to produce an odorous solid fat. This is then refined to remove the solid waxes and then deodorized to give an oil which is a white solid at room temperature and a clear liquid when melted (above 24sharpt melting point at 25°C).

data.name: Akocare™ Coconut Oil
data.description: Akocare™ Coconut Oil comes from a traceable supply chain where AAK is working on improving the trading and production conditions at origin. For example, it has been confirmed that primates are not involved in the harvesting of the coconuts, which makes the coconut oil suitable for vegans.

data.name: LIPEX® SheaClear™
data.description: Lipex SheaClear™ is a liquid ingredient suitable for clear cosmetic formulations. Lipex SheaClear™ is composed of refined, fractionated and deodorized vegetable oil from the fruit of the Shea tree (Butyrospermum parkii). Lipex SheaClear™ contains a relatively high level of unsaponifiables.

data.name: LIPEX® Cellect™
data.description: Lipex Cellect™ is a solid bioactive ingredient with caring and soothing properties based on pure vegetable lipids. Lipex Cellect™ is well characterized and documented for safe use in all type of cosmetic formulations. Lipex Cellect™ has documented anti-inflammatory, non-irritant and nonphototoxic properties. Lipex Cellect™ has a neutral odor and is yellowish in color.

data.name: LIPEX® Preact™

summary.name: Synonyms

data.description: Lipex Preact™ is a partially hydrogenated, deodorized vegetable oil from the seeds of the plant Brassica napus or campestris. Lipex Preact™ is liquid at room temperature and highly resistant to oxidation.

data.name: LIPEX® L'sens™
data.description: Lipex L´sens™ is a vegetable-based alternative to lanolin, and possesses lanolin-like properties with respect to touch, structure, gloss, film building and water absorbing capacities. It is semi-solid at room temperature and has a yellowish appearance with a neutral odor. Lipex L´sens™ is an excellent emollient thanks to its unique combination of natural glycerides from soybean and shea butter unsaponifiables.

Combined hydrophilic and lipophilic ingredients help restore natural elasticity and tone as well as prevent skin darkening, contributing to brighter, even skin tone. data.name: Evening Light Cleansing Emulsion
data.description: Evening Light Cleansing Emulsion has a milky, rich and silky smooth texture that effectively purifies skin from daylong exposure to impurities and removes all makeup, including waterproof mascara, without dehydrating the skin. It also detoxifies skin from free radicals and supports antioxidant defence. It is most suitable for end of day use as it effectively prepares skin for night care creams or our Sleep Solution Night Mask. Skin feels fresh, soft and ready for the final step in your routine.
